{
  "number": 44,
  "name": "سُورَةُ الدُّخَانِ",
  "englishName": "Ad-Dukhaan",
  "ayahs": [
    {
      "number": 1,
      "text": "Ha. Mim.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 496,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 198,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 2,
      "text": "By the Scripture that maketh plain",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 496,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 198,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 3,
      "text": "Lo! We revealed it on a blessed night - Lo! We are ever warning -",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 496,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 198,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 4,
      "text": "Whereon every wise command is made clear",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 496,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 198,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5,
      "text": "As a command from Our presence - Lo! We are ever sending -",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 496,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 198,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6,
      "text": "A mercy from thy Lord. Lo! He, even He is the Hearer, the Knower,",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 496,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 198,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 7,
      "text": "Lord of the heavens and the earth and all that is between them, if ye would be sure.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 496,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 198,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 8,
      "text": "There is no Allah save Him. He quickeneth and giveth death; your Lord and Lord of your forefathers.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 496,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 198,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 9,
      "text": "Nay, but they play in doubt.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 496,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 198,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 10,
      "text": "But watch thou (O Muhammad) for the day when the sky will produce visible smoke",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 496,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 198,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 11,
      "text": "That will envelop the people. This will be a painful torment.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 496,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 198,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 12,
      "text": "(Then they will say): Our Lord relieve us of the torment. Lo! we are believers.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 496,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 198,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 13,
      "text": "How can there be remembrance for them, when a messenger making plain (the Truth) had already come unto them,",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 496,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 198,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 14,
      "text": "And they had turned away from him and said: One taught (by others), a madman?",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 496,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 198,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 15,
      "text": "Lo! We withdraw the torment a little. Lo! ye return (to disbelief).",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 496,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 198,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 16,
      "text": "On the day when We shall seize them with the greater seizure, (then) in truth We shall punish.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 496,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 198,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 17,
      "text": "And verily We tried before them Pharaoh's folk, when there came unto them a noble messenger,",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 496,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 18,
      "text": "Saying: Give up to me the slaves of Allah. Lo! I am a faithful messenger unto you.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 496,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 19,
      "text": "And saying: Be not proud against Allah. Lo! I bring you a clear warrant.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 20,
      "text": "And lo! I have sought refuge in my Lord and your Lord lest ye stone me to death.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 21,
      "text": "And if ye put no faith in me, then let me go.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 22,
      "text": "And he cried unto his Lord, (saying): These are guilty folk.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 23,
      "text": "Then (his Lord commanded): Take away My slaves by night. Lo! ye will be followed,",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 24,
      "text": "And leave the sea behind at rest, for lo! they are a drowned host.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 25,
      "text": "How many were the gardens and the watersprings that they left behind,",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 26,
      "text": "And the cornlands and the goodly sites",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 27,
      "text": "And pleasant things wherein they took delight!",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 28,
      "text": "Even so (it was), and We made it an inheritance for other folk;",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 29,
      "text": "And the heaven and the earth wept not for them, nor were they reprieved.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 431,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 30,
      "text": "And We delivered the Children of Israel from the shameful doom;",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 432,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 31,
      "text": "(We delivered them) from Pharaoh. Lo! he was a tyrant of the wanton ones.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 432,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 32,
      "text": "And We chose them, purposely, above (all) creatures.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 432,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 33,
      "text": "And We gave them portents wherein was a clear trial.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 432,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 34,
      "text": "Lo! these, forsooth, are saying:",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 432,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 35,
      "text": "There is naught but our first death, and we shall not be raised again.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 432,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 36,
      "text": "Bring back our fathers, if ye speak the truth!",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 432,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 37,
      "text": "Are they better, or the folk of Tubb'a and those before them? We destroyed them, for surely they were guilty.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 432,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 38,
      "text": "And We created not the heavens and the earth, and all that is between them, in play.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 432,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 39,
      "text": "We created them not save with truth; but most of them know not.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 497,
      "ruku": 432,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 40,
      "text": "Assuredly the Day of Decision is the term for all of them,",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 432,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 41,
      "text": "A day when friend can in naught avail friend, nor can they be helped,",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 432,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 42,
      "text": "Save him on whom Allah hath mercy. Lo! He is the Mighty, the Merciful.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 432,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 43,
      "text": "Lo! the tree of Zaqqum,",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 433,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 44,
      "text": "The food of the sinner!",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 433,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 45,
      "text": "Like molten brass, it seetheth in their bellies",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 433,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 46,
      "text": "As the seething of boiling water.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 433,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 47,
      "text": "(And it will be said): Take him and drag him to the midst of hell,",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 433,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 48,
      "text": "Then pour upon his head the torment of boiling water.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 433,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 49,
      "text": "(Saying): Taste! Lo! thou wast forsooth the mighty, the noble!",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 433,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 50,
      "text": "Lo! this is that whereof ye used to doubt.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 433,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 51,
      "text": "Lo! those who kept their duty will be in a place secured.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 433,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 52,
      "text": "Amid gardens and watersprings,",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 433,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 53,
      "text": "Attired in silk and silk embroidery, facing one another.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 433,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 54,
      "text": "Even so (it will be). And We shall wed them unto fair ones with wide, lovely eyes.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 433,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 55,
      "text": "They call therein for every fruit in safety.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 433,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 56,
      "text": "They taste not death therein, save the first death. And He hath saved them from the doom of hell,",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 433,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 57,
      "text": "A bounty from thy Lord. That is the supreme triumph.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 433,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 58,
      "text": "And We have made (this Scripture) easy in thy language only that they may heed.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 433,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 59,
      "text": "Wait then (O Muhammad). Lo! they (too) are waiting.",
      "juz": 25,
      "manzil": 6,
      "page": 498,
      "ruku": 433,
      "hizbQuarter": 199,
      "sajda": false
    }
  ]
}